Community organizations we support and Activities we Sponsor</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Little League Ball Team</li>\r\n 	<li>Future Farmers of America</li>\r\n 	<li>Delaware Astronomical Society (DAS)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-55\" src=\"http://pandora-equator-3000.codio.io/wp-content/uploads/community.jpg\" alt=\"Local Baseball Team at Woodside\" width=\"1400\" height=\"1008\" />\r\n\r\nApproximately 30 Jersey cows make up the herd at Woodside Farm. Early in the calendar year each cow gives birth to begin the year’s milking season. Pictured at the left is the Delmarva 4H and Future Farmers of America (FFA) club conducting dairy cow judging at the farm. Through the judging process members learn much about the characteristics and nature of not only Jersey cows but other breeds as well. Their experiences expose them to judging other livestock and learning about the proper care and breeding of farm animals.','About','','inherit','closed','closed','','15-revision-v1','','','2017-04-01 14:13:21','2017-04-01 18:13:21','',15,'http://pandora-equator-3000.codio.io/index.php/15-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(121,1,'2017-04-01 14:15:00','2017-04-01 18:15:00','<strong>Open today from Noon—8 p.m.</strong>\r\n\r\nWe are <strong>open every day</strong>, including the summer holidays, <em>except Easter,</em> from <em>early April through late October. </em>We are open on weekends up till December 23. Please see our main page for special holiday hours and holiday pie pick-up times.\r\n\r\nWe serve ice cream from:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><em>Noon—8:00 p.m.</em> in the spring and fall</li>\r\n 	<li><em>Noon—9:00 p.m</em> between Memorial Day weekend and Labor Day Weekend</li>\r\n 	<li><em>Noon—7:00 p.m.</em> during our weekend hours after Halloween</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nOur creamery is located at <a href=\"https://www.google.com/maps/place/Woodside+Farm+Creamery/@39.7680416,-75.7213038,15z/data=!4m5!3m4!1s0x0:0xb6279a405da96ff3!8m2!3d39.7680416!4d-75.7213038\">378 North Star Road, Newark, DE 19711</a>\r\n\r\n<iframe style=\"border: 0;\" src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d12266.94290097768!2d-75.72130379999997!3d39.7680416!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x0%3A0xb6279a405da96ff3!2sWoodside+Farm+Creamery!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sus!4v1491069291385\" width=\"300\" height=\"150\"></iframe>','Visit','','inherit','closed','closed','','7-revision-v1','','','2017-04-01 14:15:00','2017-04-01 18:15:00','',7,'http://pandora-equator-3000.codio.io/index.php/7-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(122,1,'2017-04-01 15:27:56','2017-04-01 19:27:56','<h3><strong>Ice Cream Trailer Catering</strong></h3>\r\nWe\'ll bring our freezers and staff to serve your party, reception, or BBQ guests. Everything is included in the “per person” price.\r\n<h4>Option #1: Ice Cream Cater (Ice Cream Cups Only)</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><strong>Includes:</strong> 3–5 flavors of ice cream (your choice*), Cups, Spoons, Napkins, Full service for 1.5 hr</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Price:</strong> $450 (minimum of 100 people); $4 per person after meeting minimum.**</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4>Option 2#: Ice Cream Sundae Bar (Ice Cream with Toppings)</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><strong>Includes:</strong> 3–5 flavors of ice cream (your choice*), 3–5 toppings (your choice*), Bowls, Spoons, Napkins, Full service for 1.5 hrs</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Price:</strong> $550 (minimum of 100 people); $5 per person after meeting minimum.**</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<em>*May choose from standard list provided for that part of the season\r\n**Location may require an additional charge.\r\n</em>\r\n<h3>Party Pouch</h3>\r\n<strong>Need a sweet treat for the office or family party? The Party Pouch could be just what you\'re looking for. No fuss, no hassle, just grab it and off you go!</strong>\r\n<h4><strong>Ice Cream Party Pouch</strong></h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Includes:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>2 flavors of ice cream (within our seasonal flavor list)</li>\r\n 	<li>Cups, Spoons &amp; Napkins</li>\r\n 	<li>A Woodside Farm Creamery Ice Cream Scoop (for instant serving)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n 	<li>Ice Cream Party Party Pouch to serve <em>10 people</em> (contains 4 Quarts of ice cream)\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Picked-up* from Woodside Farm: <strong>$45</strong></li>\r\n 	<li>Delivered* (only during off-season): <strong>$50</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n 	<li>Ice Cream Party Pouch to serve <em>20 people</em> (contains 6 Quarts of ice cream)\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Picked-up* from Woodside Farm: <strong>$90</strong></li>\r\n 	<li>Delivered* (only during off-season): <strong>$95</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4><strong>Sundae Party Pouch</strong></h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Includes:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>2 flavors of ice cream (within our season flavor list)</li>\r\n 	<li>3 Toppings of your choice</li>\r\n 	<li>Whipped Cream</li>\r\n 	<li>Cups, Spoons, Napkins</li>\r\n 	<li>A Woodside Farm Creamery Ice Cream scoop (for instant serving)<em>\r\n</em></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n 	<li>Sundae Party Pouch to serve <em>10 people</em> (contains 2 Quarts of ice cream)\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Picked-up* from Woodside Farm: <strong>$45</strong></li>\r\n 	<li>Delivered* (only during off-season): <strong>$50</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n 	<li>Sundae Party Pouch to serve <em>20 people</em> (contains 4 Quarts of ice cream)\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Picked-up* from Woodside Farm: <strong>$90</strong></li>\r\n 	<li>Delivered* (only during off-season): <strong>$95</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong><em>*Please order 2–3 days ahead to allow us to accommodate your needs.</em></strong>\r\n<h3>Birthday Parties</h3>\r\n<strong>Price: $175</strong>\r\n\r\nWhat that includes…\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Rental of Party Space for 2 hours</li>\r\n 	<li>Cups of ice cream for 15 children (or 8 adults)</li>\r\n 	<li>A Woodside Creamery Staff member to scoop your ice cream as well as help you host your party.  They can assist with set-up, break-down and anything else you may need.</li>\r\n 	<li>Additional ice cream will be added to your total at $3 per child or $4 per adult.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>The Space:</strong> Separated from general customer seating by a stone wall and gates, the area will comfortably hold 75 people.\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>The Area is approximately 65 × 45 ft</li>\r\n 	<li>The party tent within the area is approx. 40× 20 ft</li>\r\n 	<li>Includes picnic tables, benches, and fold out tables if needed</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n*We do not provide and form of entertainment or tours of the farm. You are more than welcome to bring decorations, games, or any entertainment that you like! We only ask that you let us know if you have an entertainer or caterer coming so we can make any special arrangements for accommodating them.\r\n\r\n*We schedule the party area on a first come, first serve basis all throughout our season. Please call for availability and scheduling.\r\n\r\n*We do require a $75 deposit 2 weeks prior to the date of your party. This will hold the space &amp; time you\'ve requested. (Deposit will be returned to you in the event of a proper cancellation due to weather).\r\n\r\nAny other question can be directed to Mary or Gretchen in our main office at (302) 239-9847.','Groups and Catering','','inherit','closed','closed','','13-revision-v1','','','2017-04-01 15:27:56','2017-04-01 19:27:56','',13,'http://pandora-equator-3000.codio.io/index.php/13-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(123,1,'2017-04-01 17:34:13','2017-04-01 21:34:13','<table class=\"table-menu\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Cups, Cones &amp; Sundaes</th>\r\n<td>59¢ per ounce</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Quarts</th>\r\n<td>$7.25</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Pints</th>\r\n<td>$4.75</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Milkshakes</th>\r\n<td>$6.95</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Banana Splits</th>\r\n<td>$7.25</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Cow Pie Sundae</th>\r\n<td>$6</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Ice Cream Cookie Sandwich</th>\r\n<td>$4.99</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Soda</th>\r\n<td>$1</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Bottled Water</th>\r\n<td>$1.25</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Coffee</th>\r\n<td>$1.99</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Ice Cream Cakes</th>\r\n<td>6 inch $19.99\r\n9 inch $29.99\r\n¼ Sheet Cake (2 inches thick) $41.99</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Cookie Cake</th>\r\n<td>6 inch $19.99</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Ice Cream Pies</th>\r\n<td>$20</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<h3>Ice Cream Flavors</h3>\r\n<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Bacon</th>\r\n<td>As seen on Food Network’s “Unwrapped!”</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Black Raspberry</th>\r\n<td>A delightful pureed black raspberry ice cream.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Black Raspberry Chip</th>\r\n<td>Black raspberry ice cream with miniature chocolate chips.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Butter Brickle</th>\r\n<td>Butter flavored ice cream scattered with toffee pieces.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Butter Pecan</th>\r\n<td>A sweet buttery ice cream laced with pecan nut pieces.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Cake Batter</th>\r\n<td>Just like licking mom’s cake bowl as a kid!</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Cappuccino Crunch</th>\r\n<td>Cappuccino Coffee flavored ice cream with an almond toffee crunch!</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Cherry Vanilla</th>\r\n<td>Vanilla ice cream with a generous portion of dark, sweet cherry halves.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Chocolate</th>\r\n<td>Creamy chocolate ice cream.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Chocolate Almond</th>\r\n<td>Chocolate ice cream with chips of toasted almonds.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Chocolate Chip Cookie Dough</th>\r\n<td>Chocolate chip ice cream infused with pieces of chocolate chip cookie dough.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Chocolate Peanut Butter</th>\r\n<td>Peanut butter swirled in chocolate ice cream.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Chocolate Thunder</th>\r\n<td>A thunderous roar of chocolate!</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Coconut</th>\r\n<td>A coconut flavored ice cream with shredded coconut blended in.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Coffee</th>\r\n<td>Something for the coffee-holic.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Cookies &amp; Cream</th>\r\n<td>Crushed Oreo cookies in vanilla ice cream.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Cotton Candy</th>\r\n<td>The taste of cotton candy in ice cream!</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Dirt (it’s for the kids!)</th>\r\n<td>Straight out of the Woodside farm fields! Gummy worms and crushed Oreo cookies give texture to chocolate ice cream.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Motor Oil</th>\r\n<td>Coffee ice cream with a caramel &amp; fudge swirl. (The caramel is GREEN!)</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Peach</th>\r\n<td>A Delaware favorite! Peach slices in peach flavored ice cream.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Peanut Butter &amp; Jelly</th>\r\n<td>An award-winning flavor from Woodside Farm Creamery. Peanut butter and raspberry jelly to tempt your taste buds!</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Peppermint Chip</th>\r\n<td>Yes! It is pink!! Chocolate chips in peppermint flavored ice cream.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Rocky Road</th>\r\n<td>Miniature marshmallows and chocolate covered toasted almonds blended in chocolate ice cream.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Strawberry</th>\r\n<td>A strawberry flavored ice cream with delicious sliced strawberries throughout.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>No Sugar Added Black Raspberry</th>\r\n<td>A no sugar added ice cream made with pureed black raspberries.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>No Sugar Added Vanilla</th>\r\n<td>A no sugar added version of an American favorite.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Turtle</th>\r\n<td>A Woodside Farm Creamery special flavor! Toasted pecan pieces and caramel blended in chocolate ice cream.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Vanilla</th>\r\n<td>Everyone has it! Ours is made with fresh ground vanilla beans from around the globe.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/WoodsideCreamery/\">Follow us on Facebook</a> to be the first to know when we adjust our menu!\r\n<h3>Ice Cream Cakes</h3>\r\nWe are now offering Ice Cream Cakes in 3 different sizes. All three of our cakes consist of two layers of our homemade ice cream (chocolate and vanilla), divided by a layer of crushed Oreo, and wrapped in a delicious buttercream icing.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"wp-image-93 size-medium aligncenter\" src=\"http://pandora-equator-3000.codio.io/wp-content/uploads/ice-cream-cakes-300x236.jpg\" alt=\"Picture Collage of Woodside Farm Creamery’s Ice Cream Cakes\" width=\"300\" height=\"236\" />\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><strong>6 Inch Round Ice Cream Cake (3 inches thick)</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Serves 8–10 people</li>\r\n 	<li>$19.99</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>9 Inch Round Ice Cream Cake (2 inches thick)</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Serves 15–18 people</li>\r\n 	<li>$29.99</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>¼ Sheet Ice Cream Cake (2 inches thick)</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Serves 25–30 people</li>\r\n 	<li>$41.99</li>\r\n 	<li><em>Sheet Cake is available by special order only</em></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4>Instructions for Slicing</h4>\r\n<strong>You’ll need:</strong> Long bladed knife and a tall glass of hot/warm water.\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li>40–45 minutes (30 minutes for a 6-inch cake) before slicing and serving your ice cream cake, transfer the cake from the freezer to the refrigerator. (This will soften the ice cream enough to be able to cut through.)</li>\r\n 	<li>Place the knife in the glass of warm water to heat up the blade.</li>\r\n 	<li>When ready to slice and serve, remove the cake from the fridge and slice down the center of the cake. *You may need to press firmly all the way down through the two layers on the first knife insertion, pull the knife straight up and back out, and then continue across the cake in sections, to make sure you slice through the entire cake.</li>\r\n 	<li>As you slice, you’ll need to clean off your knife in the glass of warm water making sure you wip off the excess water.</li>\r\n 	<li>Top each slice with a little whipped cream, and enjoy!</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<h3>Ice Cream Pies</h3>\r\nOur farm fresh ice cream pies are 9-inches in diameter and contain approximately a quart and a half of ice cream. They are a popular holiday treat! Ice Cream Pies are available for the Thanksgiving and Christmas holidays, as well as during the summer season (personalized flavors by special request).\r\n\r\nPies are individually packaged in a clear plastic protective pie case, and come in the following flavors:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><strong>Oreo Crust</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Vanilla &amp; Chocolate</li>\r\n 	<li>Black Raspberry &amp; Chocolate</li>\r\n 	<li>Peppermint &amp; Chocolate</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Golden Graham Cracker Crust</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Pumpkin &amp; Vanilla</li>\r\n 	<li>Cappuccino Crunch &amp; Vanilla</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Orders for pies during the season will require seven (7) days advanced notice.</strong>\r\n\r\nPlease call us at <strong>302-239-9847</strong> for additional information and to place an order.','Menu','','inherit','closed','closed','','9-revision-v1','','','2017-04-01 17:34:13','2017-04-01 21:34:13','',9,'http://pandora-equator-3000.codio.io/index.php/9-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(124,1,'2017-04-01 17:35:42','2017-04-01 21:35:42','<table class=\"table-menu\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Cups, Cones &amp; Sundaes</th>\r\n<td>59¢ per ounce</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Quarts</th>\r\n<td>$7.25</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Pints</th>\r\n<td>$4.75</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Milkshakes</th>\r\n<td>$6.95</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Banana Splits</th>\r\n<td>$7.25</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Cow Pie Sundae</th>\r\n<td>$6</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Ice Cream Cookie Sandwich</th>\r\n<td>$4.99</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Soda</th>\r\n<td>$1</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Bottled Water</th>\r\n<td>$1.25</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Coffee</th>\r\n<td>$1.99</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Ice Cream Cakes</th>\r\n<td>6 inch $19.99\r\n9 inch $29.99\r\n¼ Sheet Cake (2 